ent-AU14BeltHolsterPistolUPPFull = Type 47 pistol holster rig
    .desc = This UPP-designed sidearm rig can very snugly and securely fit a Type-73, NP92, or a ZHNK-72, and their magazines or speedloaders. However, it lacks versatility in stored weaponry.
    .suffix = Full, T74, GROM

ent-AU14BeltMedicalUPPFull = Type 41 pattern medical storage rig
    .desc = The Type 41 is the standard load-bearing equipment of UPP military. It consists of a modular belt with various clips. This version is a less common configuration, designed to transport medical supplies. \nRight click its sprite and click \"toggle belt mode\" to take pills out of bottles by simply clicking them.
    .suffix = Full, GROM

